(65, 3, '2017-10-09 21:21:44', '2017-10-09 21:21:44', '<strong>Company Profile And Mission.</strong>\r\n\r\nI (Mr. PRADEEP B. NAIK), established this Company- \"PAINT REPAIR\" in 1994. I am a qualified Civil Engineer and have worked in various capacities (Site Engineer to Project engineer) with well known firms in Mumbai for the last 9 years. After having gained vast experience in this field, I started this Company. Paint Repair is duly Registered with all appropriate authorities as a proprietary firm for over 10 years.\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. PRADEEP NAIK ( MANAGING DIRECTOR )</strong>\r\nPlanning of financial management is undertaken by him &amp; plays a role in acquiring new projects and deal with clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. GAURAV NAIK ( DIRECTOR )</strong>\r\nHis planning and administration skills gives a perspective to the business execution of new projects and handling overall on going projects.\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Mission:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Commitment to quality Work and Workmanship</li>\r\n 	<li>100% guarantee of successful Project Work execution, irrespective of the associated Cost</li>\r\n 	<li>Non Disputed claim to Cost and Expenses, thus working towards the satisfaction of our Esteemed clients</li>\r\n 	<li>To believe in success rate contract business such that our Work is 100% Leak Free and the Client is always satisfied to bring us more Projects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe do a lot of Research and Development in this field. We also make our own mix of Chemicals to suit the site condition as per requirement so that we ensure The leakage is stopped permanently, We have developed a unique technique to Stop the leakage on line with in 3-5 minutes by high pressure chemical grouting System which seals the leakage 100% on the spot. Our mission is to make India leak free by the next century.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>COMPANY MANAGEMENT STRUCTURE AND TECHNICAL STRENGTH</strong></p>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-63 aligncenter\" src=\"http://pa