g area counter carefully without damaging the cuduppa. If it breaks the new stone has to be provided by the Client as per the actual bill. Taking out the whole areas plaster. Waterproofing the area. Treating with the one coat of Polymer Grout with entire required wall providing the grove for the cuduppa counter. Fixing the old existing cuduppa or provided the new one. Fixing all fitting etc. as per the requirement at site</span>.\r\n\r\n</p>', 'Waterproofing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-06 14:04:59', '2017-11-06 14:04:59', '', 13, 'http://paintrepairconsultants.com/2017/11/06/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
